column5: Got another free day without clinics, appts and errands.   Straight out the door first thing to hit a fishin hole. All sorts of pannies getting active. Even a carp  paid me a surprise visit. Silly me, forgot to take a pic with all the excitement of landing the thing on an ultralite. A nice mix of crappie.  White  and Black  and enough for a feed when the kids come home tomorrow.
